<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1452953>
    dc:description "FIGURES 165–170. leaf mines; 165: Nemorimyza maculosa (Malloch) in Erechtites hieraciifolius (transmitted light, larvae at left); 166: N. maculosa in Erigeron canadensis (reflected light); 167: N. posticata (Meigen) in Symphyotrichum puniceum (reflected light); 168: N. posticata in Teucrium canadense (transmitted light, larva at left); 169: Phytoliriomya felti (Malloch) in Pellaea glabella (reflected light); 170: P. felti in Asplenium platyneuron (transmitted light; puparia visible in four mines)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1452953/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

